Freescale's IoT Gateway BSP
===========================

To get the BSP you need to have `repo` installed. Install the `repo` utility:

$ mkdir ~/bin
$ curl https://dl-ssl.google.com/dl/googlesource/git-repo/repo > ~/bin/repo
$ chmod a+x ~/bin/repo
$ PATH=${PATH}:~/bin

Download the BSP source:

$ mkdir iotg
$ cd iotg
$ repo init -u http://<user>@sw-stash.freescale.net/scm/imx/fsl-arm-yocto-bsp.git -b jethro-4.1.15-1.0.0_ga-iotg
$ repo sync

Setup the build directory:

$ EULA=1 DISTRO=iotg-thread MACHINE=imx6ulevk-iotg . ./fsl-setup-release.sh -b <build-dir>
$ DISTRO=iotg-thread . ../fsl-iotg-internal-setup.sh

Build:

$ bitbake fsl-image-iotg-bsp
